{"title":"电焊工的心愿","authors":["郝兴卫"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"电焊工的心愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大连化学  工业公司  郝兴卫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手攀着天梯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏上云彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在碧蓝的天空上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让那繁花盛开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我栽的这朵花呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹不凋，霜打不败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是风狂雨暴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越是光彩射天外。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，祖国到处飘彩絮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命大厦长得有多快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我决心让我这焊把，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不把一根钢梁焊歪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔选自《大化职工报》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}